inn1.comm: first ball is wide outside off and Sehwag crashes it to third man
better length, just outside off and straightening, left alone
pitched up, some swing this time, he again shoulders arms
wider, tempting him to drive, the ball moves away and once again Tendulkar shoulders arms
now he plays a shot to one even wider, just opening the face of the bat and crashing the ball in front of square for four
hits a good length just outside off and shapes past the bat as he raises it above his head to leave
good length first up, some cut back in, watchfully defended
short and wide and flayed with power over backward point
good ball! Pitches just back of a length outside off and cuts in sharply, Sehwag stands there and flashes but is beaten by the sharp movement back in
that's too wide, sprayed down the pads, well taken
hits a length and he drives the ball uppishly to mid-on

short outside off, slashed off the back foot into the covers where Gibbs slides to his left and intercepts, Tendulkar sets off and gets sent back by a hesitant Sehwag but turns around and looks on as Parnell collects the ball and has plenty of time to break the sticks
pitches on a length, middle and off, and pushed to cover
hits a good spot and Karthik
sprayed down the leg side, Boucher fumbles and allows a run
short of a length, coming in, turned to short square leg
six over third man! What a shot! Saw room outside off and throws the bat it it, looking to hit over point but I'm sure he won't mind getting half a dozen
better length, Sehwag works the ball to midwicket, takes a few steps, then hesitates and Karthik, setting off, has to hurry and get back, whats happening?
outside off and holding its line to beat Sehwag's shot
punched off the front foot to the left of mid-off for one
turns the ball of the stumps to square where Bosman dives
hops back and works the ball off the pads to midwicket
short of a length and punched to the off side
hits a good length and again Karthik's drive can't beat the field
comes onto the front foot and drives the ball down to mid-off
straighter ball, some shape, Karthik shuffles and clips to midwicket
gets over the ball and clips between midwicket and mid-on
short down the pads and Sehwag gets something on it as he plays it with one hand off the bat off the hips, no chance for Boucher or the fine leg fielder
throws the bat at one wide of off and gets a single to deep point
nicely pushed down the ground but mid-on is swift to react, its Langeveldt who falls his left and saves runs
short of a length and he defends watchfully
off the mark at last with a steer down to third man for one
short of a length outside leg stump, worked to midwicket
well placed there, uses the pace to steer the wide ball off the face of the ball behind point and third man is too fine to get around
pitches and straightens, he works it off the front pad to midwicket
pitches just on leg stump and cuts back, Karthik looks to work it away but the extra bounce results in an inside edge onto the pads
beaten! Lovely length, straightens after pitching just outside off and beats Karthik all ends up
change of pace beats him again as he feebly hangs the ball outside off at one pitching wider and carrying away from him
stands nicely and punches the ball to the off side
back of a length and cramping Sehwag for room, he's keen to drive off the front foot but adjusts to check the shot, Steyn does the fielding off his boot
cuts the wide ball behind point out to the sweeper in the deep
short ball down leg stump forces Karthik to duck under it
good length just outside off and he shoulders arms
short of a length this time and he gets up to push it in front of extra cover
there's a shot! Karthik swats a short-of-a-length ball back over the umpire's head, superb hit that
straightens after pitching and he defends it back
walks out of the crease to manipulate the bowler, timing his shot well of the pads and beats midwicket, nice shot that too
uses his feet again, this time making room to crack the ball to the off side where Gibbs saves runs
banged in short and now he pulls over midwicket for two, not timed all that well but he's at least playing some shots now
good shot! Again short, again pulled, and this time with power and precision to go over midwicket
pushes it down the ground and gets a quick single
comes onto the front foot and uses the wrists excellently, turning the ball between midwicket and square leg
short of a length, this time he punches it back past Langeveldt
pitches and comes in, Sehwag mistimes the drive to midwicket
gets back and bunts the shorter ball down the ground
starts walking down, Langeveldt drags back the length and forces him to weave out of harm's way
pitches back of a length and he pushes on the rise to point
shot man! Full ball outside off and he squeezes a drive between cover and point and third man has no chance
pulls back the length and gets some cut, this time he defends
pushes hard at the ball that angles back in and mistimes it to mid-on
uses his feet to make room, drives inside-out, Gibbs dives at cover and fumbles to allow a run
short of a length, cuts back in and Karthik defends
gets up and steers a shortish ball down to third man for one
firmly driven off the front foot but cannot beat the man at cover
shorter in length and straighter too, Karthik eases back and turns the ball off his hips to raise the 50-run stand
short of a length, back goes Sehwag to steer past gully
short ball, into the ribs, nicely worked around the corner
pitches short of a length and he pushes off the front foot to cover
nicely driven on the rise but extra cover tumbles and saves runs
goes back to work a short ball off the stumps, midwicket falls across
pitches back of a length, Karthik pushes it back to Morkel
uses his feet to meet the ball and smacks it down to mid-off
fuller in length and this time he drives wide of mid-off for one
sees room outside off and crashes the drive between the covers
hits a good spot and straightens and he defends off the front foot
slightly short of a length and he pulls out to deep midwicket
short down the leg side, he goes for a shot and the ball skims the thigh pad and Boucher cannot collect
pitches on a good length and he defends it back, falling forward
full and swinging into the pads, clipped to the man at midwicket
gets up on one leg and bunts a short ball wide of midwicket
pushes at an offcutter just outside off and gets an inside edge back past leg stump
edged for four! Looks to use his crease and then slashes a short ball wide of Boucher, had a slip been there it would have been an easy catch
now he goes over mid-on's head, hitting on the rise, just clears the front leg and lets the free flow of the bat do the rest
goes for a cut and gets cramped, resulting in a chopped shot
good length ball, pushed down the track
oof! Sehwag has given that ball the treatment, making room to thrash it over extra cover for a flat six
good length ball, defended to cover point
hits a length, straightens, Karthik pushes it back, kisses Langeveldt's fingertips as it passes, then hits the stumps with Sehwag outside the crease, sad but true
pushes off the front foot, inside-edging to the leg side
flashes a short ball but cannot beat the man at cover

uses the wrists to on-drive a straighter ball down toward mid-on, sprints the first and chances Steyn's arm after he misfields while running in, he recovers and hits the stumps but Dhoni has harried home just in time
pitches back of a length, hit down to mid-off to end the over
pushed back from the crease to Morkel
tries to cut behind point but ends up inside-edging past Boucher
pitches on a good length and Karthik drives nicely to mid-off
nice and straight so Karthik can only come forward and defend
good little touch shot, coming onto the front foot and then opening the face at the last minute to procure a single to third man
cuts back in and Dhoni works the drive to midwicket
goes to pull a short ball that sits up quicker than he expected and it lobs off the glove but falls safely in front of the catchers
fuller in length, pushed with a straight bat to mid-off
gets over the bounce and uses the wrists, midwicket cuts it off
gets some room outside off and cuts out to deep cover for two
pitches it up and punches off the front foot for one
well played, gets back and works the ball past midwicket
tossed up, some turn, gets forward and drives to mid-on
bit short, Dhoni gets back, opens the face and back-cuts well
cuts again but this time into the covers
tossed up, gets some dip, Karthik makes room and slogs superbly over midwicket
flatter ball, gets across and works the ball past midwicket
tossed up again, meets it with a straight push down the track
down the pads, misses the flick, Boucher does well to take
comes onto the front foot and gets the wrists into play, working the ball to midwicket
gone! Surprised by the short ball, Karthik top-edges a hurried pull to Petersen at mid-on, easy catch off the splice of the bat and that's the third wicket down
hops across the sticks and nudges the ball to square leg
gets across and pushes the ball past midwicket, running hard
fuller in length and Dhoni punches straight to mid-off
walks across and turns the ball straight to midwicket
length ball well outside off, dabbed towards backward point for a single
a touch shorter and wide again, Dhoni lashes it to the boundary past backward point, powerful hit that
jabbed in front of point for a single this time
full and outside off, left alone by Kohli
shortish and well outside off, dabbed towards third man
length ball just outside off, driven towards cover
turned from middle stump towards wide mid-on
fullish and just outside off, pushed back to the bowler
slanting into leg, clipped to square leg for a sharp single
flicked wide of square leg this time, so there's time for a more relaxed single
fired down leg, whipped to fine leg
full on middle and leg, driven towards mid-on this time
short of length just outside off, defended towards point
sharp bouncer this time, Kohli is taken by surprise, takes the  top-edge and sails over the keeper and towards fine leg
full and outside off, driven firmly towards extra cover
back of a length and heading for off, Dhoni gets behind the line and defends
bunted towards mid-on this time, batsmen hare through for a single, Kallis seems to have hurt his hand as he belatedly and awkwardly tries to stop the throw from Parnell at mid-on
short of length, angling into off, defended towards square leg
on off stump, Dhoni makes room and slashes the ball towards point
Kohli clips it to backward square leg
Kohli gets nicely forward and opens the face of the bat to guide the ball towards backward point
length ball outside off, Dhoni punches it towards mid-off
towards mid-on this time, another single to end the over
Dhoni is gone! that is a big breakthrough, a short of length ball outside off, Dhoni seemed to be into his shot a touch early, his drive lobs towards mid-off where Albie pouches it low
back of a length on legstump, nicely glanced down to fine leg
back of length ball on middle and off, defended back down the track
length ball slanting into off, again defended down the pitch
tests him with the bouncer, batsman ducks under
short of length well outside off, slashed towards point where the fielder dives to his right to get a hand on the ball and prevent the single
on middle stump, driven down the ground, bowler gets a hand on it, the non-striker has to make get quickly back into his crease
back of a length delivery on off, Raina defends it on the off side
short of length, rising into the ribs, Raina stands tall and tucks it behind square leg
guided down to fine leg this time
a near yorker just outside off, defended towards the off side
length ball on off, tucked towards midwicket, 'No,' screams Kohli as Raina wonders whether there's a single on offer
length ball angling outside off, defended towards cover off the front foot
back of a length and just outside off, Raina gets on his toes and jabs it towards point
shortish ball angling across Raina, who chases after it in an attempt to send it towards third man, doesn't make contact

lovely shot from Raina, sensational timing, short of length ball outside off, Raina leans into a drive, hardly any effort behind that shot, was waiting for a fielder to cut it off but it goes all the way to the cover boundary
pushed to short cover off the back foot
back of length ball, moved away after bouncing, Raina is drawn towards it but he doesn't get bat on it
low full toss on offstump, defended towards cover
defended by Kohli towards backward point
fullish and outside off, flayed towards sweeper cover off
Raina gets a boundary though the timing on that lofted on-drive wasn't great, mid-on and mid-off were in the ring, just about clears the mid-on boundary and the ball trickles over the rope
just down the leg side, Raina shuffles across to get out of the way
length ball outside off, Raina moves across to get behind the line and defends solidly back down the track
short of length on the pads this time, turned towards wide mid-on
length ball on off, defended towards extra cover
Kallis teases him with a short ball again, wide outside off, Raina again attempts to dink it cheekily wide of the keeper, doesn't connect
shortish and just outside off, gets behind the line and defends
innovative from Raina, he's been trying that stroke several times now, another bouncer from Kallis, this one was close to offstump, just guides it past the keeper for four, too fine for third man
length ball outside off, mistimes an on-drive to mid-on
Raina seems to be answering questions against his ability to play the short ball here, this one is pulled powerfully, deep midwicket races across to his right but has no chance of cutting it off
overpitched outside off, crunched towaqrds short cover, where Botha moves smartly to his right to do the fielding
on middle and off this time, cautiously defended by Raina
short of length on the pads this time, Raina moves across and turns it towards the leg side
'No, no, no,' is the shout from Raina after he delicately dabs the ball towards backward point
Steyn's short ball has Raina in some discomfort, he was beaten for pace there
another short ball, Raina gets behind the line and defends more confidently this time
gets a single by turning the ball to midwicket
fired into the pads, guided to short fine leg
driven towards mid-off this time
fullish and outside off, worked towards mid-on
again on the pads, Raina gets it to the right of short third man this time to get enough time to take a single
clipped behind square leg, first runs is taken quickly but there's no time for a second
back of length and just outside off, punched towards sweeper cover off the front foot
down the leg side, Raina moved across and wanted to help that to the fine leg boundary, misses
length ball outside off, Raina moves forward and defends towards cover
back of length and just outside off, defended towards cover
shortish ball outside off, Kohli changes his shot late, swats it towards backward point
short ball just outside off, Kohli gets on his knee and sways out of the way
again it's shortish and outside off, Kohli defends towards backward point
dabbed towards mid-of, a quick single is taken
punched firmly back to the bowler
a bit of width provided, Kohli puts a lot of power behind an attempted cut but he misses the ball
whipped away towards midwicket by Kohli
full ball on off, Raina drives it towards long-on for a simple single
a tidy over from Botha comes to an end, short of length and heading for middle and off, turned towards square leg
driven on-the-up by Kohli, superbly timed to bring up his first boundary, not much footwork, Kohli drives wide of mid-off
moves across and pushes the ball towards mid-on for a single
back of a length and heading for middle and leg, Raina tucks it towards midwicket for a single
well outside off, Kohli steers the ball down to third man
short ball going down the leg side, Raina gets inside the line of that ball
turned towards deep backward square leg by Raina
length ball on the pads, pushed towards wide mid-on
Kohli eases the ball to mid-on for an easy single
full and on legstump, swept by Raina towards fine leg
a hat-trick of singles, drilled to long-on
make that four, Raina brings up the 50 partnership by punching the ball to long-off
the singles keep coming, Kohli pings the ball towards sweeper cover
heading for legstump, Raina makes room and pushes the ball towards the off side
Raina breaks the sequence of singles with his favourite shot for six, clears the front leg and swings the short of length ball over wide long-on
same length, into middle and off this time, Raina hops onto the backfoot and turns the ball towards midwicket, tight single is taken, Raina has tio dive full-length to make his ground
Kohli moves across his stumps and gets the ball towards square leg
full toss down the leg side, Raina grunts in frustration after he misses out on his attempted dab to fine leg
lovely stroke, lifts his back leg as he drives through extra cover, and that brings up India's 200
shortish ball on offstump, gets behind the line and defends watchfully
full on middle and off, Raina jabs it towards long-on for a single to end the over
lovely shot for no run, back of length heading for off, driven firmly to mid-off
short of length again, just outside off, punched towards mid-off again
same length and just outside off, Raina looks to dab it to third man, doesn't get bat on it
full and outside off, slides under Raina's bat as he looks to squeeze it towards point
on legstump,clipped off the thigh pads towards backward point for a single
short ball, Kohli is hurried into his stroke a touch, doesn't quite get hold of the ball as he pulls, the ball dribbles towards deep midwicket
short of length just outside off, gets it off the inside half of the bat towards midwicket

fantastic catch from Gibbs to break the partnership, it was a fuller delivery than the previous one, Kohli chipped it to the on-side, Gibbs leaps to his left from short midwicket and plucks a low catch
Yusuf gets off the mark by turning the ball to fine leg
good shot from Raina, who is looking very comfortable here, punched along the ground, Morkel gets a boot on it
Raina tucks it off the backfoot towards backward square leg, batsmen scamper through for the second, Parnell's throw from the deep is deflected by Boucher onto the stumps
short of length on the legstump, clipped in front of square leg this time
Raina opens the face to steer the ball towards deep backward point
back of a length just outside off, dabbed towards point by Yusuf
shortish ball outside off, Yusuf glides the ball towards short third man
a powerful hit from Yusuf, all along the ground but can't beat the man at mid-on
shortish ball angling down the leg side
a full toss, pretty high as well, probably just below the waist, surprised Yusuf who was on the front foot, manages to defend the ball though
turned in front of square leg for a single
fullish ball on middle and leg, driven uppishly towards long-on
length ball outside off, driven along the ground towards long-off
high full toss on middle and leg, Yusuf dispatches it to deep midwicket for a one-bounce four
much-better ball from Albie, but same result, a yorker outside leg, Yusuf digs it out past short fine leg for four more
length ball down the leg side, that's a wide, Albie fortunate Yusuf didn't get bat on it, that was an easy four if he connected
flatbatted towards long-on,reaches the fielder on the bounce
length ball, Raina makes room and plays an inside-out extra cover drive, long-off has to run across to his right to field
fullish ball on the legstump, clipped towards square leg
that's why Yusuf is in the team, in the slot, Yusuf effortlessly swings it over long-on for six

this time Yusuf doesn't get hold of it, it was a low full toss outside off, Yusuf was looking to hit it towards leg, the bat turned in his hand and flew towards extra cover where an overhead catch is taken, timely strike for South Africa
back of a length and angling into middle and off, defended towards mid-on
fullish ball, driven towards mid-on for another single
length ball on off, eased towards long-on for a single
down the leg side, looks to flick it but doesn't connect
full and outside leg again, poor bowling this
better line this time, but it still costs him four runs, shortish ball outside off, gets a thick outside edge which sends the ball racing ot the third man boundary
back of a length, on legstump, punched towards long-on
'No, no , no," is the call after the batsman pushes the ball towards cover point
full toss outside off, Raina looks to steer it down to third man, misses
short ball outside off, Raina attempts that innovative uppercut over slips, doesn't connect again
no problem with the connection this time, short of length, Raina swats that to the midwicket boundary to bring up his half-century
a terrific yorker to start the over, Jadeja just about keeps it out
Jadeja wants to drill that through extra cover, gets a thick inside-edge towards backward square leg
another yorker, this time on legstump, Raina punches it out towards long-on
keeps firing in the yorkers, this one was slightly down the leg side, Jadeja shuffles across and tucks it towards square leg
length ball on middle and off, driven towards wide long-on
nicely done by Raina, a length ball outside off, Raina moves towards leg to make more room and carves the ball through point for four
Jadeja plays with soft hands, the ball dribbles wide of the keeper, Jadeja wants the single but Raina doesn't
Jadeja looks to turn the ball towards the leg side but can't get bat on ball, is hit on his thigh pad
length ball on legstump, this time Jadeja gets it away with a wristy flick towards the square leg boundary, Albie dives to do the fielding

Raina was a goner if there was a direct hit there, Raina squeezes a wide, full ball towards backward point, straight to Bosman, Raina sets off for the single but Jadeja doesn't, Raina has ti turn back was miles out, but Bosman misses at the keeper's end
on the pads, helped along to fine leg
a mistimed short-arm jab from Jadeja, is in the air for a while but lands safely wide of midwicket
a slower ball from Kallis, tucked towards midwicket
fullish and outside off, driven towards mid-off
Raina looks to steer the ball to third man but misses
full outside off, Raina wafts at it, gets a thick outside edge, easy catch for Boucher, and India's chances of reaching 300 takes a hit
a short ball from Kallis, just outside off, Praveen drops the ball at his feet
down the leg side and he'll have to re-bowl that one
the angle across the batsman has Jadeja feeling for the ball outside off, unlike Raina he doesn't get an edge
a yorker on middle stump, dug out back towards the bowler
Praveen likes to swing his bat, usually likes to hit straight, this time he gets it away towards wide long-on
a powerful hit down to long-off, all along the ground, Praveen makes a bit of room to force it down the ground
Jadeja slice sa length ball over extra cover for a couple, no footwork whatsoever there

a yorker from Albie, Jadeja just about keeps it out, the ball is at his feet, he wants the single, Praveen responds early, and a sharp single is taken, Albie kicks the ball onto the keeper's stumps, third umpire is called for but Praveen has made his ground
Praveen unleashes a brutal hit down the ground, Steyn is across in a flash to cut that off just a couple of yards inside the rope

Jadeja drops the ball towards the off side, there is a some yes-no between the batsmen, Praveen is a few metres down the ground before he turns back, there's a direct hit, Praveen is in, they get an overthrow
Praveen backs away and slashes towards cover
on the thigh pad, flicked behind square leg, Langeveldt gives chase
South Africa continue to make regular breakthroughs, Jadeja goes in a similar manner to Raina, it was pitched up and outside off, Jadeja looks to drive, gets an outside edge to the keeper
length ball on off, defended back towards the bowler
another yorker, Praveen was backing away, Steyn followed him, dug out behind square leg
length ball outside off, poked towards cover point
Nehra is clearly no comfotable facing Steyn, a full ball on middle and leg, Nehra shuffles across and blocks towards long-on
short ball outside off, Nehra lets it through to Boucher

some comical running here, Nehra pushes the ball to mid-on, Nehra and Praveen both set out, Nehra decides he can't make it so he holds up his hand asking Praveen to go back, Nehra also scampers back, there's a direct hit at the keeper's end, there was no appeal for a run-out but replays show Nehra's bat was only on the line and not across it
short ball, Nehra gets it away towards short fine leg
a good old fashioned tailender's swing to a short ball, nowhere near the ball, I enjoy watching tailender's bat
he's off strike now, squeezed towards point by Nehra
length ball outside off, Praveen clears the front leg and slices it towards deep point
again Praveen backs away towards leg and drills the ball powerfully, down towards long-on
Nehra shows he can hit, swings at a length ball, Nehra backed away and swung powerfully at it, made great contact and the ball sails over wide long-on
Nehra retians strike by dabbing a yorker outside off towards backward point
Steyn sends down a quick yorker, too quick for Nehra, just outside off, goes through to the keeper

horror running from India again, Nehra slogged a full toss towards midwicket, Bosman fields and a direct hit at the non-striker's end would have ended Nehra's stay but he misses and Steyn can't collect it either
shortish ball outside off, Praveen can't connect
super bowling from Steyn, a yorker on legstump, Praveen manages to get it towards mid-on
low full toss outside off, Nehra pokes it towards third man
good shot for a single, Praveen muscles the ball to sweeper cover after making room
full and outside off, Praveen, as usual, backed away, tries to slash that one but doesn't connect

the comedy running finally results in a wicket, a back of length outside off, Praveen swats it to long-off, he wants the second and is on his way, Nehra then sends him back, a great throw from de Villiers from the deep, Langeveldt does the rest
whoah, this is unbelievable, a yorker on off, 136kmh, Nehra misses, the ball kisses offstump and races away for four, the bails don't fall, that is bizarre, Langeveldt  can't believe it
swing and a miss outside off
again Nehra is beaten outside off
low full toss driven down to long-on for a couple, India finish on 298

inn2.comm: nips back in and keeps very low, phew that as close to the off stump
nice inswing on the pads and he clips him wide of square leg
lands it outside off and gets outswing this time, safely left alone
tries to work it to the on side but gets a leading edge to the off side, or maybe not, I think it clipped his pad
swings it away from the right-hander and left alone
Big Appeal: Swings it in late and has the batsman lunging forward, the ball hits the base of the pad and he shuffles across his stumps, was it outside the line of off? Maybe
drifts on the pads and he runs it down to fine leg

Nehra thinks he's edged it but Tarapore shakes his head! Gibbs slashes away from his body and the ball doesn't bounce as much, big deviation off the under edge of the bat, the keeper and Nehra are certain about it, lucky escape for Gibbs
stays behind the line and defends
drifts on the pads and he tucks it to deep square leg
expansive drive but gets a thick inside edge onto his pads
not too much bounce there and he punches it towards mid-off
comes on straight and he clips it to square leg
on the pads and he tucks it off his pads down to fine leg
gets well forward and defends to the off side
gets well forward and defends to the off side
misfield by the substitute Abhishek Nayar at square leg, 2 bonus runs there
defended down the track
stand and hit, stays at the crease and launches into a pitched up delivery, lofts through the line to wide long-on
slower ball and the ball takes the inside edge and nearly lobs back to the stumps
extra bounce this time and it catches Gibbs by surprise, hangs his bat out outside off
gets beside the line and taps it down to point

Appeal Times the punch very sweetly towards mid-off and Jadeja catches Bosman being very casual in getting back to his crease, there's a direct hit and Bosman just about, and I mean JUST about gets his bat past the line, close call for the 3rd umpire
gets beside the line and chops it down to point
stays behind the line and taps him down to mid-off
drifts on the pads and he clips it hard and straight to fine leg
nervy moment for Gibbs, he loosk to loft over mid-off but mistimes it, the ball swirls to the left of mid-off
the slower ball and he picks it early, reaches out and fetches it from outside off and scoops him over mid-on
down the leg side and wide called
stays behind the line and punches to mid-off
Sreesanth starts off with a wide down the leg side, close to the batsman's glove
nice timing, turns the face of the bat only slightly and ensures the ball hits the middle of the bat and races wide of midwicket and mid-on
that's a Gibbs special! Stays at the crease, doesn't move his feet, swings effortlessly at a good length delivery outside off and bangs it over deep midwicket
gets forward and pushes it just wide of mid-off
punchy drive towards mid-off and Raina charges from short cover, dives full length and in one motion aims at the bowler's stumps, good fielding there,
clips it down to midwicket and no run taken
even better than his previous four, Sreesanth drifts just a bit on middle and leg and a defensive clip is enough to beat mid-on and race away, the outfield does the rest
crack! Short and wide outside off, he reaches out and puts a lot of power behind that shot and slaps it past point and cover
the fine leg's up and Kumar drifts on the pads, he easily clips it wide of him and the ball races away
stays beside the line and defends to the off side
taps it to the off side
tries to whack it to fine leg but he mistimes it and the ball rolls to the fielder
good length on middle and leg and tucked away down to midwicket
loose shot, gets a bit of width outside off and he slashes hard and misses
tucks it behind square on the on side, he has protection at the boundary
skids towards the off stump and he just about manages to keep it away
one tight slap! Gives him a bit of width outside off and Bosman stays at the crease and gives it everything, beats the gap at the covers and races away
on the body and he shovels it over square leg
stays on the back foot and punches it down to Jadeja at mid-off
slower ball and he makes room but doesn't control the loft well, the ball just clears mid-on
swings and misses and Dhoni whips off the bails, Bosman's foot never left the crease, the 3rd umpire takes a look
